strings: <voice_0x01001D0F><se_high>media princess: Cash & Carry passed the test with flying colours. Is not that great?
<voice_0x01001D10><se_high>media princess: Now they can continue together in their father's business.
<voice_0x01001D11><se_high>media princess: Pretty close, because there are all kinds of arguments.
<voice_0x01001D12><se_high>media princess: we used to fight remember when we were children
<voice_0x01001D13><se_high>media princess: I've always seen you as a brother.
<voice_0x01001D14><se_high>media princess: But now I see you more as a person
<voice_0x01001D15><se_high>media princess: I mean, alright, I forgot what I said. enjoy the night
